## 📊 Model Details

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Algorithm | Random Forest Classifier |
| Training Samples | 4920 |
| Features | 17 symptoms |
| Classes | 41 diseases |
| Accuracy | 100% (test set) |
| Dataset Source | Kaggle — itachi9604 |

